ISLAMABAD, Jan 17 (APP):Pakistan Navy (PN) Commodore Muhammad Faisal Abbasi was promoted to the rank of Rear Admiral on Friday.
He is graduate of PN War College Lahore, NDU Islamabad and has vast experience of various Command & Staff appointments, said a PN spokesman in a tweet.
